Upgrade Jetty to 10.0.11 (#181)

* disable sni host check per default
* add sni option documentation and add sni required option as well
* do not build with java 8
* default http compliance same as jetty9
* use jetty bom
* remove enforcer exclusions not needed anymore for bytecode check
* exclude jetty-annotations from the dependencies as it is not needed
* jdk17 profile not needed anymore
